Text.val: 11.05.2011 SH SCR16448 Replaced GNRL_CURRENCY by ADMN_CURRENCY
... PI.DisplayedLevel = 'W' means totals are calculated over the whole client,
only in case if called from ICA302E

ExpSyntax.val: 'DEBC_ADMNO ='&Trim (Str ({0,7},'4'))&' and DEBC_CLNTNO ='&Trim (Str ({0,8},'5'))&' and DEBC_DATDELETED is null'

SQL_STMT_U.val:
select aa.AMOUNT_NOT_H,aa.AMOUNT_NOT_C, aa.COUNTER_NOT, aa.FACACC_NOT, bb.AMOUNT_30_H, bb.AMOUNT_30_C, bb.COUNTER_30, bb.FACACC_30, cc.AMOUNT_60_H, cc.AMOUNT_60_C, cc.COUNTER_60, cc.FACACC_60, dd.AMOUNT_90_H, dd.AMOUNT_90_C, dd.COUNTER_90, dd.FACACC_90, ee.AMOUNT_120_H, ee.AMOUNT_120_C, ee.COUNTER_120, ee.FACACC_120, ff.AMOUNT_120G_H, ff.AMOUNT_120G_C, ff.COUNTER_G120, ff.FACACC_G120, gg.AMOUNT_TOTAL_H, gg.AMOUNT_TOTAL_C, gg.COUNTER_TOTAL, gg.FACACC_TOTAL
from
(select cast(sum(A.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_NOT_H, cast(sum(A.INVO_AACTUALC) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_NOT_C, COUNT(*) COUNTER_NOT, cast(sum(AAA.INVA_ACTAFACTORING) as decimal (13,2)) FACACC_NOT from :1/DEBC join :1/INVO A on A.INVO_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO and A.INVO_AACTUALI <> 0 and days(':2') - days(A.INVO_DUEDATE) <=0 :6 join :1/INVA AAA on AAA.INVA_NO = A.INVO_NO and AAA.INVA_CURRENCY = ':3' :5 where :4) aa
join
(select cast(sum(B.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_30_H, cast(sum(B.INVO_AACTUALC) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_30_C, COUNT(*) COUNTER_30, cast(sum(BBB.INVA_ACTAFACTORING) as decimal (13,2)) FACACC_30 from :1/DEBC join :1/INVO B on B.INVO_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO and B.INVO_AACTUALI <> 0 and days(':2') - days(B.INVO_DUEDATE) between 1 and 30 :6 join :1/INVA BBB on BBB.INVA_NO = B.INVO_NO and BBB.INVA_CURRENCY = ':3' :5 where :4) bb on 1=1
join
(select cast(sum(C.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_60_H, cast(sum(C.INVO_AACTUALC) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_60_C, COUNT(*) COUNTER_60, cast(sum(CCC.INVA_ACTAFACTORING) as decimal (13,2)) FACACC_60 from :1/DEBC join :1/INVO C on C.INVO_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO and C.INVO_AACTUALI <> 0 and days(':2') - days(C.INVO_DUEDATE) between 31 and 60 :6 join :1/INVA CCC on CCC.INVA_NO = C.INVO_NO and CCC.INVA_CURRENCY = ':3' :5 where :4) cc on 1=1
join
(select cast(sum(D.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_90_H, cast(sum(D.INVO_AACTUALC) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_90_C, COUNT(*) COUNTER_90, cast(sum(DDD.INVA_ACTAFACTORING) as decimal (13,2)) FACACC_90 from :1/DEBC join :1/INVO D on D.INVO_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO and D.INVO_AACTUALI <> 0 and days(':2') - days(D.INVO_DUEDATE) between 61 and 90 :6 join :1/INVA DDD on DDD.INVA_NO = D.INVO_NO and DDD.INVA_CURRENCY = ':3' :5 where :4) dd on 1=1
join
(select cast(sum(E.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_120_H, cast(sum(E.INVO_AACTUALC) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_120_C, COUNT(*) COUNTER_120, cast(sum(EEE.INVA_ACTAFACTORING) as decimal (13,2)) FACACC_120 from :1/DEBC join :1/INVO E on E.INVO_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO and E.INVO_AACTUALI <> 0 and days(':2') - days(E.INVO_DUEDATE) between 91 and 120 :6 join :1/INVA EEE on EEE.INVA_NO = E.INVO_NO and EEE.INVA_CURRENCY = ':3' :5 where :4) ee on 1=1
join
(select cast(sum(F.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_120G_H, cast(sum(F.INVO_AACTUALC) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_120G_C, COUNT(*) COUNTER_G120, cast(sum(FFF.INVA_ACTAFACTORING) as decimal (13,2)) FACACC_G120 from :1/DEBC join :1/INVO F on F.INVO_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO and F.INVO_AACTUALI <> 0 and days(':2') - days(F.INVO_DUEDATE) > 120 :6 join :1/INVA FFF on FFF.INVA_NO = F.INVO_NO and FFF.INVA_CURRENCY = ':3' :5 where :4) ff on 1=1
join
(select cast(sum(G.INVO_AACTUALH) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_TOTAL_H, cast(sum(G.INVO_AACTUALC) as decimal (13,2)) AMOUNT_TOTAL_C, COUNT(*) COUNTER_TOTAL, cast(sum(GGG.INVA_ACTAFACTORING) as decimal (13,2)) FACACC_TOTAL from :1/DEBC join :1/INVO G on G.INVO_DEBC_NO = DEBC_NO and G.INVO_AACTUALI <> 0 :6 join :1/INVA GGG on GGG.INVA_NO = G.INVO_NO and GGG.INVA_CURRENCY = ':3' :5 where :4) gg on 1=1
for fetch only
